      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/y/839c29/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-10-17T01:22:38.151Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi there,</p>\n<p>I tried to jump on to Trainer Day for my first session today, having previously used Zwift.</p>\n<p>I have a Wahoo Kickr Snap V2, Favero Assioma Uno power pedals, using the Android app and am syncing workouts through Training Peaks.</p>\n<p>On the first ride I started my warmup, pedalling quite firmly but the reading only showed about 50 watts. I know from Zwift and from outside riding that this was off. Then, I noticed that under Power Match, the reading looked more accurate (screenshot below is of me at \u2018121 watts\u2019 according to Trainer Day, then +116w at 235w in the Power Match section).</p>\n<p>ERG mode was also definitely not working as my wattage was not even close to steady.</p>\n<p>It felt like I was pedaling through concrete just to keep the wattage at a decent rate. This was just the warmup so didn\u2019t bother going any further.</p>\n<p>The question is, what am I doing wrong? Really hoping to use this as much as possible in the next few days so a quick fix would be welcomed!</p>\n<p>Cheers<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/60ba5f4c55d74e0e2127a3405a3b48785d4090de.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/60ba5f4c55d74e0e2127a3405a3b48785d4090de\" title=\"ERG example\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/60ba5f4c55d74e0e2127a3405a3b48785d4090de_2_690x310.jpeg\" alt=\"ERG example\" data-base62-sha1=\"dNH8y1XWG5AkDEFZHXbuhTz259s\" width=\"690\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/60ba5f4c55d74e0e2127a3405a3b48785d4090de_2_690x310.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/60ba5f4c55d74e0e2127a3405a3b48785d4090de_2_1035x465.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/60ba5f4c55d74e0e2127a3405a3b48785d4090de.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/60ba5f4c55d74e0e2127a3405a3b48785d4090de_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">ERG example</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7576 63.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
