      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/57b2e6/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-10-17T08:49:28.448Z",
      "cooked": "<p>FYI: there are multiple ways to handle this. When connected with ANT+, there is no problem. Single or double, ANT+ handles all that. But BLE connection has no standard way of doing this. You could change the setting in your Assioma app to send double single sided, it will only do it on the BLE channel. Or you can do it in the TrainerDay app.<br>\nThere are cycling apps that don\u2019t have the setting and then you can only correct by setting it in the Assioma app.<br>\nSo it\u2019s up to you to decide where you correct for it.</p>",
